\id 3JN - Asang Khongca Bible (2019) 
\h 3 Johan 
\toc1 3 Johan 
\toc2 3 Johan 
\toc3 3 Jhn 
\mt1 3 JOHAN  
\ipq Diotrephe loe kricaa zaehoikung kacoehta ahmin amthang kami ah oh, anih loe ahmuen maeto hoi maeto bangah tamthanglok thui (Johan mah oep kaom kami, tiah thuih ih Demetrius kalang mue, tiah poekhaih tawnh o) kami to talawk han koeh ai. To pongah Johan loe Kaia, tiah kawk ih, ahmin amthang kami kalah maeto khaeah Diotrephe mah talawk han koeh ai ih kami to kahoihah khetzawn hanah ca tarik pae.  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Tsk 19.29; Rom 16.23; 1 Korin 1.14.\x*Kricaabu zaehoikung kacoehta mah, loktang ah ka palung ih Kaia khaeah,  
\v 2 kang palung ih kami, kahoih poekhaih palungthin na tawnh baktih toengah, hmuennawk boih ah qoengh moe, ngan na tui thai hanah lawk kang thuih pae, tiah ca tarik.  
\v 3 Loktang loklam to na pazui moe, loktang lok ah na oh, tiah nawkamyanawk angzoh o moe, ang thuih o naah, paroeai anghoehaih ka tawnh.  
\v 4 Ka caanawk loktang thungah caeh o ti, tiah ka thaih naah, to anghoehaih pongah kalen kue anghoehaih ka tawn ai boeh.   
\s1 Thapaekhaih hoi kasaethuihaih  
\p
\v 5 Palung ih kami, nawkamyanawk hoi angvinnawk khaeah, oep kaom ah tok na sak;  
\v 6 nihcae mah nang ih amlunghaih to kricaabu hmaa ah thuih o boeh: nihcae mah Sithaw koehhaih baktiah tamthanglok taphong o hanah na bomh thaih nahaeloe, kahoih hmuen ah ni om tih:  
\v 7 nihcae loe Anih ih ahmin hoiah ni caeh o, Gentelnawk khae hoi abomhaih tidoeh la o ai.  
\v 8 Loktang toksahkung ah a oh o thai toeng hanah, aicae mah to baktih kaminawk to abomh han oh.  
\v 9 Kricaabu khaeah ca ka tarik: toe nihcae zaehoikung ah kaom, Diotrephe mah kaicae talawk han koeh ai.  
\v 10 To pongah, kang zoh nahaeloe, a sak ih hmuen to ka panoek sak han, anih loe aicae kasae thuih khue ai ah, nawkamyanawk doeh talawk han koeh ai: nawkamyanawk talawk han koeh kaminawk doeh pakaa moe, nihcae to kricaabu thung hoiah pathok ving.  
\v 11 Palung ih kami, kahoih ai hmuen to pazui hmah, kahoih hmuen to pazui ah. Kahoih hmuen sah kami loe Sithaw ih kami ah oh: toe kahoih ai hmuen sah kami loe Sithaw to hnu ai.  
\v 12 Kaminawk boih mah Demitria hoihaih kawng to thuih o, loktang lok mah doeh anih hoihaih kawng to thuih: ue, aicae mah doeh kahoihah a thuih o; a thuih o ih lok loe loktang ni, tito na panoek.  
\v 13 Ca zetpui tarik han ka koeh, toe cacung hoi catui hoiah tarik ka koeh ai:  
\v 14 nang hoi angqum palang tih hmang, tiah oephaih ka tawnh, to naah mikhmai kang tongah lok aram tih hmang.  
\v 15 Nang khaeah monghaih om nasoe. Aicae ampuinawk mah ban ang sin o. Toah kaom ampuinawk to ka hmin hoiah ban sin ah.   